{"tid":1281834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁家輝 你記唔記得1937年7月7日","createTime":"2019-07-03T11:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T14:10:29.000Z","uid":191568,"like":91,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"34258c965e921f299333d4b13e3db7707838c523","tid":1281834,"uid":191568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:37:09.000Z","msg":"因為深夜食堂的原創是源自大日本帝國。<br />\n<br />\n如果中國人收看深夜食堂，即表態支持大日本帝國。<br />\n<br />\n因為連你入場睇，即代表支持套戲。<br />\n<br />\n換句話黎說，大日本帝國比中國好。 <br />\n<br />\n中國永遠排第二，因為是抄的。<br />\n<br />\n日本帝國是排第一的 是原創的。<br />\n<br />\n1937年 7月7日是盧溝橋 呢個時候 <br />\n<br />\n中國讓深夜食堂翻版<br />\n<br />\n打進中國市場 你對得住當年為我們抗日的義士嗎？<br />\n<br />\n梁家輝 你自導自導咁抄日本原創電影 <br />\n<br />\n仲係呢個敏感時期出 你係咪想我們中國同胞 <br />\n<br />\n一邊為義士禱告，默哀 ,一邊不齒日本的罪行，<br />\n<br />\n一邊支持日本？"},{"pid":"1b71aa8e00c569ee34aa484ee56cb58655fcd492","tid":1281834,"uid":191568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:41:02.000Z","msg":"puah"},{"pid":"ac1e9e9fd6fc32062f4ee634388bdd49af6b3abc","tid":1281834,"uid":191568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:41:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"783aded5d8df2d00da9654ce372ab0762aceb671","tid":1281834,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:41:45.000Z","msg":"係佢微博貼"},{"pid":"22b014c5d3ebcb65e12d784d43cd310b2e2ae272","tid":1281834,"uid":191568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4297502af0cdbd080174ff887e2c274b8f3bee5a","tid":1281834,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:46:24.000Z","msg":"叛我中華者，雖遠必誅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd0626ba8902bc63dc7cdd686e2684b693a8cad","tid":1281834,"uid":191568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"783aded5d8df2d00da9654ce372ab0762aceb671","tid":1281834,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:41:45.000Z","msg":"